invocation.excerpt: This will start a training session in the GPU. First it will pre-train the generator using MSE error for 2 epochs, then it will train the full GAN (generator + discriminator) for 100 epochs, using content (mse + vgg) and adversarial loss. Although weights are already provided in the repository, this script will also generate them in the checkpoints file.
Other training parameters are the default of train script
